OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FFog and low cloud burning off
OL,6,Fthis morning but may linger across the
OL,7,FWestern Isles, Skye and the Sutherland
OL,8,Fcoast for a while. Otherwise dry and
OL,9,Fsunny, and becoming warm. Cooler
OL,10,Fonshore breeze along the Moray Firth
OL,11,Fcoast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,14,Fsome late sunshine. Then the rest of
OL,15,Fthe night will be dry with patchy mist
OL,16,Fand low cloud. Chilly night in the
OL,17,Feast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
