OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FOnce again a dry, warm and
OL,6,Fsunny day after any mist or low cloud
OL,7,Fclears in the morning. Breezy at times
OL,8,Faround coasts and exposed higher
OL,9,Fground.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMainly
OL,12,Fdry, bright and warm on Friday but
OL,13,Fcloudier with the chance of a shower
OL,14,Flater. Cooler and cloudier over the
OL,15,Fweekend with a chance of showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
